  m_text: Welcome to Net Profits, the fishing and money making game! Start off by
    heading to the bank and taking out a loan. The max amount you can take out at
    once depends on your current profits. Use your loan to buy your first boat, and
    get fishing! A percentage of each catch will go towards paying back your loan.
    Once your loan is paid off, head to the Boats menu to start investing your money.
    Good luck!
